# textdomain: mcl_monster_eggs
Hides a silverfish=Skriva srebrno ribico
An infested block is a block from which a silverfish will pop out when it is broken. It looks identical to its normal counterpart.=Okužen blok je blok, iz katerega skoči srebrna ribica, ko se ga uniči. Videti je enak svoji običajni različici.
Infested Stone=Okužen kamen
Infested Cobblestone=Okužen tlakovec
Infested Stone Bricks=Okužena kamnita opeka
Infested Cracked Stone Bricks=Okužena razpokana kamnita opeka
Infested Mossy Stone Bricks=Okužena mahovita kamnita opeka
Infested Chiseled Stone Bricks=Okužena izklesana kamnita opeka